Name: Amy's Camden
Info: Her nights out playing pool at Hawley Arms pub and indulging in all the excesses that sadly led to her demise, made Amy Winehouse a legend of this historic part of London. Come and visit the spots linked to the life of the remarkable British singer and unofficial Queen of Camden. You'll find traces of Amy everywhere.
